jose̩f dunyi po̩tife̩r
oñ ma mu jose̩f du gwo̩ru nyijipti taku po̩tife̩r onoji fero ki chagboji amaganyiwñ ki che̩ne̩ ijipti mu gba la kwo̩wo̩ abo ishmae̩l ku ma du gwo̩ru nyo̩mo̩

tak oduwñ li ka ku jihofa dugbowñ i ño̩ li ka ku jihofa la je̩ ñw e̩wñ du ki che ra nyu o̩wo̩
oñ i li jose̩f eju jose̩f la che̩wñ ñw u oñ i mowñ du chadejutunyiwñ e̩wñ du ki ne̩ i la ko jef o̩wo̩wñ

jose̩f la che̩neju e̩nyo̩ año̩lawñ achuto̩

oñ o̩jo̩ka i le tef unyi ki chuko̩lo̩wñ aboke̩le̩ unyi le̩ du def unyi o̩mo̩ n
onobule̩ le̩ gwo̩nyukpowñ kakini e̩ bumi dachi i muda tukpowñ no̩ nyu o̩wo̩ i ra le to̩lo̩fe̩
oñ e̩gba ki li ki tukpowñ no̩ nyu o̩wo̩ ki ra to̩fe̩
i la nomudala do̩ aboke̩le̩ unyiwñ i ka ñwu ma kakini me̩ go owñ de̩ne̩ hibruka wugbo wa ki chuwa uke̩ i wejefu ugbo mi ki bumi dachi tak omi domu nyate̩ akpogu
oñ abu ki gbo̩ abu chomu nyate̩ akpogu i te̩wñ o̩lawñ no̩ nyumi o̩wo̩ oñ i ra le to̩lo̩fe̩

tak i ño̩ ka ñw u alu ki ka le̩ kakini adu abo hibru ke̩ du wugbo wa le̩ wa ejefu ugbo mi ki che mi uke̩
abu ku domu nyate̩ akwa i la te̩wñ o̩lawñ no̩ nyumi o̩wo̩ oñ i ra to̩lo̩fe̩
oñ abu koduwñ gbo̩ o̩la ko̩yawñ ka ñw u kakini alu kaduwe̩ che mi de̩ uwe̩do̩wñ mutajo
tak odu jose̩f mowñ du tef unyi uga ugbo ku ma ji ame̩namu eonu jo̩ abe̩le̩ i def unyi uga o̩mo̩

agboji unyi uga le̩ dejuwñ ge̩wñ du ki do̩wo̩ jose̩f ge̩ n todabu ki jihofa dugbowñ e̩wñ du ki ache jihofa la je̩ ñw u ki ra ñw u
jose̩f dunyi uga akoji o̩na ñwu ma
oñ i lewatanubi e̩wñi ke̩ne̩ ki adomi ñw onu ijipti ñmo̩ kpai e̩ne̩ ki ache uje̩wñ egini ñw u fo̩la che bi oduma onu ijipti le̩ eju
taku fero we̩do̩ ramonojiwñ mejii owñ chagboji abo ku ma domi ñw u ñmo̩ kpai agboji abo ku ma che uje̩wñ egini ñw u je̩
oñ i muma ko nyone̩ o̩wo̩ ef unyi agboji amaganyi le̩ ef unyi uga ugbo ku ma ji jose̩f te̩
tak agboji amaganyi mudu edejute̩ ma du ñwu jose̩f oñ i che e̩wñ ñwu ma ma jef amu le̩ kpo̩kpe̩ pe̩
tak ejejima fo̩na na e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ no̩na ewñ odu o̩jo̩ okate e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ nalu koji o̩nawñ ki na de̩ owñ chadomi ñw onu ñmo̩ kpai ache uje̩wñ egini eonu ijipti ku ma ji ma jef unyi uga le̩
taku jose̩f wejefu ugbo ma odudu oñ i li ma go ejuma che̩bu nyo̩wo̩
tak i tamonoji fero ku ma jef o̩wo̩ one̩ ef unyi oduwñ kpowñ ene kakini e̩wñ chi kejume̩ chekpa jo̩ abe̩i eñinii
taku ma ka ñw u kakini a fo̩na na i la ne̩ne̩ du ki neke kojiwñ ñwa n taku jose̩f ka ñwu ma kakini i cho̩jo̩ noji e̩wñ eka n narodubume̩ ku me̩ ka ñwu mi
tak agboji abo ku ma domi ñw onu ñmo̩ mo̩nawñ du ka ñwu jose̩f i ka ñw u kakini ef o̩nami go ikeli achiwebe̩te̩maka do̩gbami
ikeli achiwebe̩te̩ma le chene̩to̩ me̩ta oñ i dabe̩ne̩ ki abu ebuwñ mutu dufu ugbo ki mujo̩ mujo̩ le i me̩ro achiwebe̩te̩ma ki kpa ko dufu
ago omi fero la def o̩wo̩mi oñ u me̩ro achiwebe̩te̩ma le̩ ko ufu pili nyef ago omi efero tak u mago le̩ du to̩wo̩ fero
taku jose̩f ka ñw u kakini ojiwñ de̩ e̩te̩ me̩ta le̩ cho̩jo̩ me̩ta
gbogbo tak o̩jo̩ me̩ta ki jo̩ fero aduwe̩ oji dago ki aduwe̩ dabi te̩gu uguguwe̩ oñ uwe̩ adago fero to̩wo̩wñ alu ki de̩ o̩gbo̩gba e̩gba kuwe̩ domi ñw u ñmo̩ le̩
ama uwe̩ ki nadibekado mi e̩gba ki ra ñw e̩ narodube̩ ke̩ che̩nyo̩ ñwu mi ke̩ minabalimi du ñwu fero ke̩ mumi gba kwef unyii dufu
todu eji ma mumi ji kwoj ane̩ abo hibru temi ge̩ u la che e̩wñ du taku ma dumi tef urai n
egba kagboji abo ku ma che uje̩wñ egini le̩ li koji o̩nawñ ki ka chenyo̩ i ka ñwu jose̩f kakini omi ño̩ fo̩na na ge̩ go agba akala efufu me̩ta la jojimi
oñ ef agba ki date̩ otitala uje̩wñ egini ku ma che ojoji ojoji du jefuwñ todu fero oñ ame̩we̩ jaje̩ kwef agba ki dojimi

oñ i maboke̩le̩ me̩lu chi kwef amo̩mayewñ ki ko ma wugbo fero ki ma ma
taku fero ka ñw amo̩mayewñ kakini obe e̩wñ me̩ che taku ma ka ñwu fero kakini amaduwe̩i chamadide ame̩wño̩re egini tawa tamatawa
ma ño̩ ka ñwu fero kakini a lewa ka ge̩ne̩ ane̩i todu ugbo kame̩wño̩re amaduwe̩ egini ajije̩ de̩ ge̩ n todu ukpo̩ta akpa ololo ane̩ kenan todule̩ a rodube̩ ke̩ je̩ ñw amaduwe̩ gugu ane̩ goshe̩n
taku fero ka ñwu jose̩f kakini atawe̩ kpai amo̩mayewe̩ lewa ugbowe̩ me̩
ane̩ ijipti te̩ ñw e̩i ugbo kane̩ nyo̩ tule e̩ datawe̩ kpai amo̩mayewe̩ gugu je̩ ñwu ma gugu ane̩ goshe̩n i la che̩wñ ke̩ ma abo ki le efuma mak e̩ ko ma chamagboji abo ku ma de ame̩wñ ukpa emi
taku jose̩f mu jeko̩b atawñ duwa oñ i mu du gugu o̩gba fero taku jeko̩b kadua ñwu fero
oñ fero ka ñwu jeko̩b kakini o̩do̩ onu ma bie̩

taku jeko̩b ka ñwu fero kakini o̩do̩ o̩jo̩ ege̩ne̩mi ku ge̩ne̩i cho̩do̩ o̩gbo̩ me̩fa nyoke me̩gwa o̩jo̩ o̩do̩ udejumi la wewe n i ño̩ che̩bie̩ne̩ i la tu alu o̩jo̩ o̩do̩ udeju amatami ef ege̩ne̩ ku ma ge̩ne̩ le ta n
taku jeko̩b kadua ñwu fero oñ i kwo̩gba fero dufu
taku jose̩f hiatawñ kpai amo̩mayewñ gugu i la bane̩ ñwu ma ku ma ne̩ ane̩ ijipti ugbo kane̩ nyo̩ tule oj ane̩ ramese̩s alu ku fero ñwa te̩
oñ jose̩f duje̩wñ ñw atawñ kpai amo̩mayewñ kpai abo unyi atawñ du je̩ alu kuwewe abo unyi unyima de̩
uje̩wñ ño̩ bo̩ ane̩ o̩mo̩ du ge̩ n todu ukpo̩ta le̩ akpa ololo oñ o̩la abo ane̩ ijipti kpai abo ane̩ kenan muda noji ukpo̩ta ki akpa
jose̩f la mo̩ko̩ du ku ma li ane̩ ijipti yajo̩ kpai eane̩ kenan tod e̩wñ e̩yo̩ ku ma la oñ jose̩f mo̩ko̩ le̩ ko wef unyi fero
tak e̩gba ku ma mo̩ko̩ du ki dane̩ ijipti ko la e̩wñ kpa kpai eki dane̩ kenan abo ane̩ ijipti chaka lewugbo jose̩f ma kakini duje̩wñ ñw a e̩wñ chi ka ku rinyo̩ ejuwe̩i todu o̩ko̩wa takpa
taku jose̩f kakini o̩ko̩me̩ takpa maku me̩ kame̩wñ ukpame̩ wa tak u naduje̩wñ koji ñwu me̩

abe̩le̩ ma kame̩wñ ukpama wugbo jose̩f taku jose̩f kuje̩wñ koji amanyama kpai koji ame̩wñ ukpa ki chala kpai ewo kpai ame̩wñ ukpa ki chokuno̩ kpai amo̩ke̩ke̩te̩ ñwu ma abe̩le̩ i kuje̩wñ ñwu ma je̩ koji ame̩wñ ukpama du o̩do̩ le̩

e̩gba ko̩do̩ le muda ma ño̩ lewugbowñ o̩do̩ ekeji ma la ka ñw u kakini awa adu maja ñw odumi alu ka ko̩ko̩wa la e̩wñ kpa n ame̩wñ ukpa ki chabe̩re̩me̩le̩ du la mud eodumi e̩wñ du bo̩ eju odumi n chai año̩lawa kpai ane̩wa kate
tode̩wñ a ku rinyo̩ ejuwe̩ meji tawa tane̩wa fawa kpai ane̩wa la tod uje̩wñ tak awa kpai ane̩wa ache amadu ñwu fero e̩ la mulu e̩wñ ko ñw a ka deju ka we eku todu kane̩ ki we echalache̩
abe̩le̩ jose̩f fane̩ ijipti du la ñwu fero todu e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ abo ijipti du mane̩ uche̩wñ duta todabu kukpo̩ta akpa ololo oñ ane̩ le̩ mud efero
i cheamone̩ le̩ i muma ko kpe̩ jo̩ ewo ewo kwo alo̩me̩ ane̩ ijipti oka gbogbo walo̩me̩ ekeji
chai ane̩ amatama kate oñ i ma gba la n todu amatama che̩no̩da ema ugbo fero ma la je̩ e̩wñ o̩da ema ku fero du ñwu ma todule̩ oñ ma ma kane̩ma ta n
taku jose̩f ka ñw amone̩ le̩ kakini me̩ go omi fame̩ kpai ane̩me̩ la ñwu fero eñini go ulu e̩wñme̩ de̩ ku me̩ gbe̩ ane̩
oñ i awatu e̩gba ku me̩ ako e̩wñ oko wunyi ame̩ ki kukpe̩ e̩ke̩lu ñwu fero oñ ukpe̩ me̩le̩ kibo̩ acheme̩ o̩to̩to̩lame̩ todu ulu oko kpai uje̩wñme̩ todu abo unyime̩ kpai uje̩wñ todu abome̩ egini
taku ma kakini uwe̩ mojiwa gba te̩ me̩ odumi ki li wa eju dee mak amadu fero awa che ke
taku jose̩f mele̩ du che̩wñ uhio̩me̩ ane̩ ijipti gbogbo tojolu eñini ka ku fero anukpe̩ e̩ke̩lu e̩wñ du chai ane̩ amatama kate ma chefero n
abe̩le̩ israe̩l gugu ijipti oj ane̩ goshe̩n oñ ma chane̩ e̩wñ ene̩ o̩mo̩ ma la bi o̩ma oñ ma wewe nyo̩gba ololo
jeko̩b la do̩do̩ me̩gwebie ane̩ ijipti abe̩le̩ o̩jo̩ jeko̩b owñ cho̩do̩ ki da tak i ku cho̩do̩ o̩gbo̩ mebie nyoke mebie

oñ iko e̩gba kisrae̩l adiñmi me̩ru awa i la fo̩mawñ jose̩f do̩ wa i ka ñw u kakini iche̩wñ ke̩ li mi eju narodube̩ e̩ ki do̩wo̩we̩ nutami ka ke̩ che e̩wñ e̩nyo̩ kpai ochochi ugbo mi narodube̩ e̩ ki du mi ji ane̩ ijipti n
ama e̩gba ku kwo dachi manyamatami uwe̩ ki mumi du kw ijipti alo ke̩ mumi du ji ane̩ ojinoji amatami tak i dohi nache alu ke̩ ka
tak i kakini e̩ fu go̩ ñwu mi oñ i fu go̩ ñw u tak israe̩l fojiwñ dalo̩ noji ate̩wñ le̩
jeko̩b kadua ñwu manasa kpai ifraim
oñ i lewatubi e̩wñ le̩ ge̩ ke̩ne̩ka ka ñwu jose̩f kakini go atawe̩ acho̩ga tak i mamo̩mawñ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ meji manasa kpai ifraim ko rubi alo
oñ ma ka ñwu jeko̩b kakini go o̩mawe̩ jose̩f awugbowe̩i tak israe̩l feju gbiti gugu oj ate̩
oñ jeko̩b ka ñwu jose̩f kakini o̩jo̩ odobao̩gagu do̩lawñ tejugede ñwu mi luz oj ane̩ kenan i la de̩nyo̩ ñwu mi
oñ i ka ñwu mi kakini go nakamo̩ma ñw e̩ wewe naje̩ ñw e̩ wewe nyo̩gba naño̩ duwe̩ che o̩wo̩ amone̩ oñ nadane̩ kide̩ ñw ugbe̩we̩ ubiwe̩ ku ma ne̩ ogbegbele̩
fai amo̩mawe̩ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ meji eku ma bi ñw e̩ ane̩ ijipti o̩gba tak u wugbowe̩ ijiptii chemi ifraim kpai manasa achemi alu ku rube̩n kpai sime̩o̩n de̩
tak ekuwe̩ adato̩ bi ubima achewe̩ oñ ma adodu amo̩mayema manyu ma ef e̩wñ oguma
i chemi e̩gba ku kwo padan wa reche̩l leku bumi te̩ ane̩ kenan ej o̩na o̩mo̩ e̩gbale̩ ule̩ e̩frat bo̩ re ta oñ u mu du ji o̩na e̩frat o̩mo̩ owñ che be̩tle̩he̩m
tak israe̩l go amo̩ma jose̩f e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ le̩ i kakini abo ugbo de̩i
taku jose̩f ka ñw atawñ kakini amo̩mami ko̩jo̩ ko ñwu mi emi jo̩i oñ i kakini narodube̩ ke̩ ko ma wugbo mii ku nakadua ñwu ma
abu keju israe̩l gbe̩ noj ogijowñ i neke li e̩wñ n taku jose̩f muma ko me̩ru ugbowñ oñ i dalu kuma alu i la gba ma ke̩do̩
tak israe̩l ka ñwu jose̩f kakini ibe dedumi efu ka ku nali ejuwe̩ n e̩ la go o̩jo̩ ño̩ je̩ ñwu mi li ugbe̩we̩ ge̩
taku jose̩f muma ko kwo agadawñ dufu i te̩kpe̩ gbogbo wa fejuwñ bane̩ ma
taku jose̩f mama meji ko ifraim do̩wo̩ awo̩to̩wñ ugbo o̩wo̩ awohi israe̩l manasa la do̩wo̩wñ awohi ugbo o̩wo̩ israe̩l awo̩to̩ oñ i muma ko me̩ru ugbowñ
tak israe̩l no̩wo̩ awo̩to̩wñ dala i mu du ne̩ ifraim eki chimo̩to̩ oji o̩wo̩ awohiwñ la noji manasa i gwejugede do̩wo̩wñ kofi omune̩ da todu manasa cho̩mo̩gba
tak i kadua ñwu jose̩f i kakini o̩jo̩ ekamatami ebraham kpai aise̩k lule̩ o̩gbawñ le̩ o̩jo̩ eki ne̩ mi akwe̩gba ku ma bi mi gbogbo teñini
onuche̩ o̩jo̩ eki gba mi tane̩ bef e̩wñ e̩bie̩ne̩ du te̩ owñ le̩ ki de̩nyo̩ ñw abokolobiai ama ki dodumi manyu ma kpai odu amatami ebraham kpai aisek ama ki mud o̩wo̩ one̩ o̩ge̩ge̩de̩ ile̩i
tak e̩gba ku jose̩f li katawñ do̩wo̩wñ awo̩to̩ noji ifraim i bie̩ne̩ ejuwñ tak i gwo̩nyu o̩wo̩ atawñ ki mu du boji ifraim te̩ toji manasa
oñ jose̩f ka ñw atawñ kakini atami i chabe̩le̩ no todu ekide̩ cho̩mo̩gba mo̩wo̩ awo̩to̩we̩ du no oji
atawñ muda ko̩ oñ i kakini u chema o̩mami u chema owñ le año̩ chuche̩ amone̩ kpo̩fo̩ owñ año̩ chelile ge̩ okekelewñ muda anana towñ le oñ ugbe̩wñ amud ukpe̩ko̩ amone̩ uche̩ uche̩
abe̩le̩ i kadua ñwu ma o̩jo̩ le̩ i kakini lugbo we̩ oñ abo israe̩l akadua kakini o̩jo̩ ki je̩ ñw e̩ ke̩ dab ifraim kpai manasa abe̩le̩ i dugugu ifraim to̩gba ñwu manasa
tak israe̩l ka ñwu jose̩f kakini go eku nakui o̩jo̩ muda adugbo we̩ i aduwe̩ dabi tane̩ amatawe̩ ge̩
u la mukpe̩ ane̩ka komi no̩kwo̩chagelimi kpai o̩o̩do̩mi babo amo̩r le̩ gba du ñw e̩ tamo̩mayewe̩ le
jeko̩b kadua ñw amo̩mawñ me̩gweji
taku jeko̩b nomudala do̩ amo̩mawñ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ i kakini me̩ do̩lame̩ jeju ku naka ñw me̩ e̩wñ ki ake̩re̩bume̩ e̩gba o̩jo̩ otitala

aboi chaka cho̩lo̩pu israe̩l me̩gweji e̩wñ katama ka ñw ma abu ki akadua ñw ma la de̩ alu ke̩nyo̩ e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ de̩ i du ñw ma
tak i ñwa ñw ma i ka ñw ma kakini ma che ku ma mumi du amanyu abomi fumi ji ugbo amatami ef owo ki doko ifro̩n abo he̩t le̩
ef owo ki doko makpila eki do̩wo̩ olodudu mamre ane̩ kenan ekebraham la manyu oko le̩ kwo̩wo̩ ifro̩n abo he̩t todu ki nugbo ki aji oku abowñ
o̩mo̩ ma febraham kpai sara o̩yawñ ji o̩mo̩ ma faise̩k kpai ribe̩ka o̩yawñ ji o̩mo̩ omi la du lea ji ge̩—
ma la oko le̩ kpai owo ki defuwñ o̩wo̩ amo̩ma he̩t
tak e̩gba ku jeko̩b foji e̩ñwa ki ñwa ñw amo̩mawñ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ le̩ kpa i me̩re̩wñ ko joj ate̩ i miñmiwñ da oñ ma mowñ du amanyu abowñ
ma du jeko̩b ji—jose̩f leku
taku jose̩f lewa batawñ eju ma i kworakuwñ oñ i daluwñ ko̩ alu
taku jose̩f ñwa ñw abuko̩lo̩wñ ku ma chamobochi ku ma datawñ kpe̩ka abe̩le̩ amobochi le̩ misrae̩l du kpe̩ka
oñ o̩jo̩ o̩gbo̩ mejiwñ jo̩ todu abe̩le̩ o̩jo̩ ku ma du kpe̩ka ajo̩ abo ijipti la dekuwñ o̩jo̩ e̩te̩gwa
tak e̩gba ko̩jo̩ eku ede̩wñ jo̩ jose̩f ko̩la ñw abo unyi fero kakini iche̩wñ ku me̩ li mi eju narodubume̩ ku me̩ ko̩la nyu fero eti kakini
atami je̩ ñwu mi go̩ i kakini go eku naku ef urami ekomi gwa ñw o̩lami ane̩ kenan o̩mo̩ e̩ dumi ji todule̩ ifai narodube̩ ke̩ je̩ ñwu mi nyate̩ o̩mo̩ ku fatami ji tak u nadakubiwa ge̩
taku fero kakini te̩gu nyo̩mo̩ ke̩ fatawe̩ ji alu ki je̩ ñw e̩ go̩ le̩
abe̩le̩ jose̩f mute̩gu le ki datawñ aji abuko̩lo̩ fero chaka kpai abogijo unyiwñ kpai abogijo ane̩ ijipti chaka du mute̩gu le kpai owñ
kpai abo unyi jose̩f chaka kpai amo̩mayewñ kpai abo unyi atawñ chai abimo̩to̩ma egini kpai ame̩wño̩re̩ma egini kpai amokuno̩ma ma to̩no̩ jane̩ goshe̩n
to̩ko̩ane̩ ogu kpai amananya mute̩gu le kpai owñ ma la cho̩wo̩ one̩ o̩temeje
taku ma lewa ugbo ajita atadi ugbo ku ma gwo̩ka eki dudaba jordan o̩mo̩ ma dinaku inakuwñ chenana ololololo oñ i deku atawñ o̩jo̩ mebie
e̩gba kabo ane̩ le̩ abo kenan ma che e̩gba ku ma li eku ku ma de̩ ugbo ajita atadi le̩ ma kakini eku kide̩ chekpuna ugbo abo ijipti todule̩ ma dodu o̩mo̩ ko̩ ebe̩lmizraim i dudaba jordan
abe̩le̩ amo̩mawñ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ le̩ la che ñw u alu ki ñwa ñwu ma
todu amo̩mawñ mowñ du tane̩ kenan ma la fu ji ef owo oko makpila ekebraham la manyoko o̩wo̩ olodudu mamre o̩wo̩ ifro̩n abo he̩t le̩ todu ki ne̩ ugbo ki akabowñ ji
taku abu ku jose̩f fatawñ ji owñ kpai amo̩mayewñ mudabi nyijipti kpai abo du ku ma le bowñ nyaji atawñ
tak e̩gba kamo̩maye jose̩f li katama leku ma kakini ikani jose̩f achulaka wa ki ade̩bie̩ne̩ du ka cho ruwa o̩me̩ kpa
oñ ma kpuche̩ nyugbo jose̩f kakini atawe̩ ñwa ñw a o̩gba tak i ku kakini

abu ku me̩ aka ñwu jose̩f de̩ kakini narodube̩ fai ke̩ me̩do̩ kpako kamo̩mayewe̩ che̩ du chuma ele kpai adurema todu ma che̩ e̩bie̩ne̩ gbe̩ tak ifai a rodube̩ ke̩ me̩do̩ kpako kamadu o̩jo̩ eatawe̩ che̩ le̩ du chuma ele jose̩f la mutaku e̩gba ku ma ko̩la ñw u
tak amo̩mayewñ ño̩ lewa bane̩ ma o̩gbawñ oñ ma kakini go amaduwe̩ a che
taku jose̩f ka ñwu ma kakini me̩ ki railo n todu omi koji o̩jo̩
i cheme̩ e̩bie̩ne̩ ame̩ ñwa nyumi o̩jo̩ muda fu ñwa re̩nyo̩ todu ki mudu che alu ki de̩ eñini ki famone̩ wewe jadu kojima ki do̩mo̩

e̩wñ o̩la arama rod aro̩n kpai amo̩mawñ

uwe̩ ki ga e̩wñ o̩la kiafo̩ todu aro̩n o̩mayewe̩ todu ojima kpai alifia

ma la agba o̩jamalia kpai odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju

i ane̩ e̩wñ ojikawñ meji ki che̩gametiwñ meji ku ma ane̩ ga momune̩

oñ igbe̩chi uje̩do̩ ku ma fu hi o̩ka ki do̩lawñ ku ma du lago uko̩lo̩wñ adabu uko̩lo̩ e̩fo̩d onugo i achalu okate kpai owñ eo̩jamalia eodufa kpai ekpikpa odufa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩
tak uwe̩ ki kokuta one̩ks meji ke̩ la fodu amo̩ma e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ israe̩l ko̩ nyo̩lawñ
oduma me̩fa ajo̩la okutaka oñ odu ama me̩fa ki bo̩ ajo̩la okuta ekeji alu ku ma bi ma aro̩ne aro̩ne
alu ke̩ne̩ ki agbe̩ okuta agbe̩ e̩wñ uhiuko̩ alu le̩ uwe̩ ki kodu amo̩ma israe̩l nyokuta le̩ meji e̩ ki fo̩jamalia da nyago̩go̩wñ me̩le̩
tak e̩ ki mokuta meji le̩ ko noji e̩wñ ojika e̩fo̩d le̩ ki chokuta urewa todu amo̩ma e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ israe̩l aro̩n la anoduma oj ikawñ meji wa o̩gba jihofa todu urewa
uwe̩ ki la fo̩jamalla da ke̩wñ le̩ ki gugu efuwñ
kpai iyagba o̩jamalia ki de̩ hiolo meji uko̩lo̩wñ adabe̩ne̩ kiku ku ma ba nyo̩nyo̩ tak e̩ ki fiyagba ku ma ba le̩ ji me̩wñ ugugu ojika le̩

tak uwe̩ ki che̩wñ ube̩do̩ma eoji ajo̩ eka uko̩lo̩ e̩ne̩ ki cho̩ka i ache uwe̩ ache ki dab uko̩lo̩ e̩fo̩d le̩ e̩ ki la no̩jamalia kpai odufa kpai ekpikpa odufa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ che
e̩guche̩nowñ ago̩go̩wñ me̩le̩ achokujo̩ ujijiwñ la cho̩chalika unabe̩wñ la cho̩chalika
uwe̩ ki la kokuta nyefuwñ o̩gba o̩gba me̩le̩ o̩gbawñ ejodudu che sardius kpai topaz kpai karbunke̩l
o̩gbawñ ekeji ache e̩me̩rald kpai safaya kpai daimo̩nd

uwe̩ ki la no̩jamalia ki de̩ hiolo chiyagba ki dab iku tod e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩
uwe̩ ki la chelika o̩jamalia meji jo̩la e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ ke̩ la felika meji le̩ ro̩ teti e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma meji
tak uwe̩ ki miyagba o̩jamalia meji le̩ ko tunyelika meji ki jo̩la e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ etiwñ meji
oji iyagba meji ku ma ba ki bo̩ tane̩ e̩ mu du ro nyo̩jamalia ku ma da nyokuta le̩ ke̩ ko jojika e̩fo̩d atama ej o̩gbawñ
tak uwe̩ ki chelika o̩jamalia meji ke̩ ko ele̩ jiba e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma mejeji e̩ ko jetiwñ ejefu ki kado e̩fo̩d le̩

taku ma ado̩jaja odufa ki dab iku ki nabe̩ pe̩ tunyelikawñ ku ma fe̩wñ ube̩do̩ma ji manye̩fo̩d ki no̩la e̩wñ ujiñmi ku ma hi o̩ka o̩la e̩fo̩d le̩ todu ke̩wñ ube̩do̩ma ki we etu be̩fo̩d te̩
abe̩le̩ aro̩n anodu amo̩ma e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ israe̩l ef e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma eoji ajo̩ eka abe̩do̩wñ ma e̩gba ki alo tef uña kiafo̩ le̩ todu ki che̩wñ urewa o̩gba jihofa o̩ko̩ko̩lo̩

ma la aje̩ e̩wñ ku ma ne̩ che̩wñ uboma le̩ ku ma ko nyuma o̩wo̩ e̩ko̩ ku ma laño̩ che ma ku ma fo̩ e̩ne̩ ejaduña muda aje̩ ele̩ n todu i afo̩
i la che̩wñ ke̩la ku ma ko nyuma o̩wo̩ e̩ko̩ abe̩k uje̩wñ le̩ bo̩ nyodudu e̩gba le̩ e̩ ki fabubo̩wñ gujo ef una ma ki je̩ ele̩ n todu i afo̩
abe̩le̩ uwe̩ ache ñw aro̩n kpai amo̩mawñ owñ chalu du komi ñwa ñw e̩ le̩ o̩jo̩ mebie e̩ ke̩wñ nyuma o̩wo̩ e̩ko̩
o̩jo̩ du e̩ ki du o̩kokuno̩ wa chiche̩bo̩ adure ki che̩wñ eboma uwe̩ ki ño̩ gwubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ rinyo̩ e̩gba ke̩ che e̩wñ uboma toduwñ ke̩ la fekpo ba to̩lawñ ke̩ che ki fo̩
e̩ ki che e̩wñ uboma todu ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ o̩jo̩ mebie ke̩ che ki fo̩ tak ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ afo̩ eefo̩ e̩wñ du ki akadubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ afo̩
e̩wñ kuwe̩ la adu wa chiche̩bo̩ oj ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ de̩ amo̩mala meji ku ma cho̩ma o̩do̩ka o̩do̩ka e̩ ko wa che o̩jo̩ñwa o̩jo̩ñwa o̩ko̩ko̩lo̩

ujijiwñ ki cho̩hibo̩wo̩ka unabe̩wñ ki la chohibo̩wo̩ka ago̩go̩wñ me̩le̩ ki chokujo̩ o̩gbawñ ki la chohibo̩wo̩ meji igbawñ ki chalu okate kpai owñ
e̩ ki la ko̩jamalia ki de̩ hiolo lamo̩lawñ tojiwñ takolowñ daka kpai igbawñ tak uwe̩ ki fo̩jamalia gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ ke̩ du lametiwñ daka
e̩ ki laño̩ che elika meji toduwñ o̩gane̩ o̩jamalia pe̩te̩ke̩ ke̩ du lamo̩ le̩ akolowñ meji eji e̩ che jo̩ ele̩ achugbo ku ma dugbo̩lo̩ oli tunyu ku ma ne̩
e̩ ki la doli akesia che ugbo̩lo̩ oli le̩ ke̩ do̩jamalia wenyu
tak e̩ mu du dago o̩gba ukpo ugbeju eki dugbo akpati ibenu le̩ o̩gba ugugu unye̩do̩ ki boji e̩wñ ibenu le̩ ma ugbo komi ade kpai uwe̩
tak aro̩n ake̩wñ kwe̩ kwe̩ kwe̩ ki akpo wa gujo ojiwñ odudu du e̩gba karo̩n do̩mo̩ añwagege che e̩gba le̩ i agu e̩wñ e̩kpo le̩ jo ojiwñ
oñ ane̩ odu e̩gba karo̩n aduna tagege le̩ i ñagujo ki mud e̩wñ ki akpo o̩gba jihofa gbogbo nyo̩hio̩gume̩ o̩ko̩ko̩lo̩
e̩ ki ke̩wñ ejaduña ki akpo kpai e̩wñ egujo n kpai e̩wñ ele wa che ki te̩gu kwojiwñ n e̩ ki la de̩wñ wa danyojiwñ n
aro̩n la ache̩wñ e̩boma oj igbawñ onuka o̩do̩ka i ane̩bie̩ e̩wñ ku ma duwa tod adure ee̩wñ e̩boma le̩ che e̩wñ e̩boma toduwñ onuka o̩do̩ka gbogbo nyo̩hio̩gume̩ e̩wñ efo̩ eefo̩ todu jihofa i che
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini
e̩gba ke̩ kamo̩ma israe̩l aluka e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ ade̩wn uloji o̩lawñ tane̩ ñwu jihofa e̩gba ke̩ kuma aluka todu ke̩wñ bie̩ne̩ ki we ebuma ma e̩gba ke̩ kuma aluka
e̩wñ ke̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ ku ma kaluka adu wa de̩ ukpe̩reji she̩ke̩l alu ki she̩ke̩l euña kiafo̩ de̩ she̩ke̩l le̩ che gera ogu ukpe̩reji she̩ke̩l ki che̩wñ edu nyate̩ ñwu jihofa
e̩ne̩ du ko̩do̩wñ jo̩ ogu ef abo ku ma kaluka le̩ adu e̩wñ edu nyate̩ ñwu jihofa le̩ wa
anana aduwa tule n e̩nubie̩ aduwa ki anyaru ukpe̩reji she̩ke̩l le̩ e̩gba ku me̩ ke̩wñ ku me̩ du nyate̩ le̩ wa ñwu jihofa le̩ ku me̩ che̩wñ e̩boma tod amonugome̩ n
uwe̩ la agbo̩ko̩ e̩boma le̩ kwo̩wo̩ amo̩ma israe̩l ke̩ la ko̩ko̩ le̩ jo̩ todu uko̩lo̩ unyabo ujeju todu ki che̩wñ urewa amo̩ma israe̩l o̩gba jihofa kame̩ ki che e̩wñ e̩boma todu onugome̩
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini
uwe̩ ki ño̩ debijeikpa che ukpachi ugwo̩wo̩ kpai e̩wñ ki agugu ojiwñ o̩mo̩ ma agwo̩wo̩ e̩ ki dele̩ gugu agbagba unyabo ujeju kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ke̩ la chomiofo nyu
aro̩n kpai amo̩mawñ agwe̩ o̩wo̩ma kpai e̩re̩ma o̩mo̩
e̩gba kuma nyef unyabo ujeju kpai e̩gba ku ma te̩me̩rubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ku ma che e̩wñ egujo ñwu jihofa ama anomiofo agwe̩ ku ma we eku
abe̩le̩ ma agwe̩ o̩wo̩ma kpai e̩re̩ma ku ma we eku eie̩ achuhio̩me̩ o̩gbegbele̩ owñ chewñ kpai eugbe̩wñ gbogbo nyo̩hio̩guma
jihofa ño̩ ka ñwu mose̩s kakini
uwe̩ ki me̩wñ ido̩ro̩ eo̩me̩me̩le̩ ko emur ki chomi ki chalu she̩ke̩l oli me̩gwa esinamo̩n ki akpo ki chukpe̩reji alu le̩ owñ choli me̩lu ekalamus ki akpo ki chalu she̩ke̩l oli me̩lu
e̩kasia la chalu oli me̩gwa e̩ñwawñ chalu ku she̩ke̩l euña kiafo̩ de̩ kpai ekpo o̩lif e̩ñwa hin oka
e̩ kele̩ che ekpo kiafo̩ ku ma du ba to̩la e̩wñ ma agwe̩gwa nyomune̩ alu kabo ku ma cho̩ka otulale ache ekpo efo̩ ku ma ba te̩wñ o̩la i che
uwe̩ ki dele̩ kulu o̩la unyabo ujeju kpai akpati ibenu le̩
kpai itebulu kpai ane̩wñ chaka kpai akete manyane̩wñ chaka kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ugbo ku ma gu e̩wñ ki akpo jo le̩
kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ee̩wñ e̩gujo ojiwñ le̩ manyane̩wñ du kpai ukpachi ugwo̩wo̩ kpai e̩wñ ki gugu ojiwñ le̩
uwe̩ la ache e̩wñ le̩ du ki fo̩ ki mud e̩wñ ki afo̩ e̩efo̩ e̩wñ du ki kado abele̩ afo̩
uwe̩ ki la fekpo ba to̩la aro̩n kpai amo̩mawñ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ ke̩ che ma ku ma fo̩ ku ma chamatama kama ki che e̩wñ ñwu mi
tak uwe̩ ki ka ñw amo̩ma israe̩l kakini ekide̩ achekpo kiafo̩ todu mi ku ma ba te̩wñ o̩la gbogbo nyo̩hio̩gume̩
ma adele̩ danyaño̩la one̩ n me̩ ki la che e̩go̩wñ n owñ chugbo e̩wñ ki jefuwñ efo̩ i afo̩ e̩wñ ki afo̩ i ache ñwu me̩
e̩ne̩ ki fe̩go̩wñ che abe̩k e̩ne̩ du ki mu du to̩la e̩ne̩ ejaduña re ma ake̩ne̩ le̩ da bamone̩wñ te̩
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini me̩wñ ido̩ro ki akpo ko owñ che stakte̩ kpai onicha kpai galbanum e̩wñ ido̩ro̩ ki akpo le̩ manyu frankinse̩ns ki de̩ hiolo e̩ñwa e̩le̩ e̩le̩wñ achokujo̩
ke̩ mele̩ ko che e̩wñ ku ma gujo ki akpo ku ma che likpa alu kabo ku ma cho̩ka otulale ache omu ki che̩buru i de̩ hiolo i la fo̩
e̩ bu kwefuwñ ke̩ fu gwu ne̩ke̩ne̩ke̩ ke̩ du kwefuwñ to̩gba e̩wñ ibenu ef unyabo ujeju ugbo komi ade kpai uwe̩ e̩wñ ki afo̩ eefo̩ ñwu me̩ i che
oñ e̩wñ ku me̩ che ku me̩ gujo ki akpo le̩ me̩ ki che e̩go̩wñ alu ki gwe̩gwanyomune̩ ñw o̩lame̩ n e̩wñ kiafo̩ ñwu jihofa ugbo me̩ i che̩
e̩ne̩ du ki ache e̩go̩ ele̩ ki gbo̩ e̩kpowñ ma ake̩ne̩ le̩ da bamone̩wñ te̩
ma chi be̩zale̩l kpai oholiab tod uko̩lo̩ unyabo
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini
go omi fodu be̩zale̩l o̩ma uri o̩ma he̩r ki chabo o̩lo̩pu juda do̩
omi la je̩ ñw u kpe̩ko̩ ñw afu o̩jo̩ kpai ibe kpai oji o̩la ema kpai e̩wñ ema kpai emeju uko̩lo̩ e̩wñ ojoji ojoji du eche
ki ñwa uko̩lo̩ o̩ka ki che uko̩lo̩ o̩jamalia kpai ajifa kpai ebijeikpa
kpai okuta eda ku ma du tunye̩wñ kpai igbo oli efa ki chuko̩lo̩ ojoji ojoji du
e̩ la go omi foholiab o̩ma ahisamak ki chabo o̩lo̩pu dan chi manyu u laño̩ dibe tibe tef e̩do̩ amone̩ chaka ku ma nibe efu ku ma ki che e̩wñ du komi ñwa ñw e̩
unyabo ujeju kpai akpati ibenu kpai ugugu unye̩do̩ ki dojiwñ kpai ane̩ unyabo le̩ chaka
kpai itebulu le̩ kpai ane̩wñ kpai akete hiolo le̩ manyane̩wñ chaka kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ku ma gu e̩wñ ki akpo jo ojiwñ
kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ e̩wñ egujo manyane̩wñ chaka kpai ukpachi ugwo̩wo̩ kpai e̩wñ ki agugu ojiwñ
kpai otogbo ku ma hi reju kpai otogbo eefo̩ todu aro̩n atama le̩ kpai otogbo amo̩mawñ ku ma ne̩ che e̩wñ atama
kpai ekpo ku ma ba to̩la kpai otulale ki akpo todu uña kiafo̩ likpa alu du komi ñwa ñw e̩ ama ki che
o̩jo̩ uñmi ede
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini
uwe̩ ki ño̩ ka ñw amo̩ma israe̩l kakini ame̩ ki fo̩jo̩ uñmimi de chuu todu owñ chujiwe ki tagbagba omi kpai ame̩ gbogbo nyo̩hio̩gume̩ todu kame̩ ki ma ka komi jihofa ache me̩ ku me̩ fo̩
abe̩le̩ ame̩ ade o̩jo̩ uñmi todu i afo̩ todu me̩ e̩ne̩ du ki fu daji ekpa ma akpa e̩ne̩ du ki fuko̩lo̩ka che o̩jo̩ le̩ ma akonugo e̩ne̩ le̩ da bamone̩wñ te̩
o̩jo̩ me̩fa oñ ma achuko̩lo̩ kade o̩jo̩ e̩kebiewñ muda cho̩jo̩ uñmi euñmi kiafo̩ todu jihofa e̩ne̩ du ki fuko̩lo̩ du che o̩jo̩ uñmi ekpa ma akpa
todule̩ oñ amo̩ma israe̩l ade o̩jo̩ uñmi ku ma dejute̩ o̩jo̩ uñmi gbogbo nyo̩hio̩guma ki mud alo ekpe̩ ogbegbele̩
owñ chujiwe ki tagbagba omi kpai amo̩ma israe̩l ogbegbele̩ todu o̩jo̩ me̩fa jihofa che efojale kpai ane̩ile̩ tak i ñmi o̩jo̩ e̩kebie oñ i riñmi
e̩gba ki foluka che kpai mose̩s oj uwo sainai kpa i la malo ibenu meji le̩ ko ñw u alo okuta i che o̩wo̩ o̩jo̩ ko̩
abo israe̩l dojikane̩ ñw o̩mokuno̩ o̩jamalia

tak e̩gba kamone̩ le̩ li ka ku mose̩s kpo̩kpe̩ egwo̩ru kwoj uwo wane̩ amone̩ le̩ fo̩lama do̩ jeju wugbo aro̩n oñ ma ka ñw u kakini kwane̩ ke̩ famo̩jo̩ che ñw a kama ki tuwa o̩gba i chemose̩s ki ko wa kwane̩ ijipti dufu wai a mema abu ki le n
tak aro̩n ka ñwu ma kakini file̩li o̩jamalia ki deti amo̩yame̩ kpai eamo̩mame̩ e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ kpai onobule̩ le̩ jada ku me̩ mu ko wa ñwu mi
abe̩le̩ amone̩ le̩ chaka file̩li o̩jamalia ki detima jada oñ ma mu ko wugbo aro̩n
tak i mu gba kwo̩wo̩ma oñ abu ki fu da o̩ma okuno̩ i la nadude̩ finawñ ko̩ taku ma kakini abo israe̩l amo̩jo̩me̩ ku ma ko me̩ kwane̩ ijipti dufu wa de̩
oñ abu karo̩n li i fubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ne o̩gbawñ tak aro̩n fakoyawñ ta kakini o̩na chuje̩wñ uyo̩ ñwu jihofa
taku ma takpa kwane̩ o̩jo̩ñwawñ oñ ma me̩wñ e̩gujo kowa che ma ño̩ ke̩wñ ure̩do̩ wa ge̩ oñ amone̩ le̩ gugu ane̩ ku ma je̩ e̩wñ ku ma ñmo̩ taku ma kwane̩ achiya
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini gwo̩ru tane̩ alo todu amone̩we̩ kuwe̩ ko kwane̩ ijipti dufu wa le̩ fo̩lama kpabie̩ me̩

ma hika muna bo̩na komi ñwa ñwu ma te̩ piopioi ma fo̩ma okuno̩ da ñw o̩lama oñ ma dojikane̩ ñw u ma la fe̩wñ e̩bie̩ kpa ñw u oñ ma kakini ame̩ abo israe̩l amo̩jo̩me̩ ku ma ko me̩ kwo ane̩ ijipti dufu wa jo̩i
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini u famone̩i li me̩ e̩ la go amone̩ ku ma fo̩lo̩ma lo dago ma che
todule̩ ifai e̩ tumi no̩ kuwe̩do̩mi ki tajo buma ma una una todu ku fuma lie̩ tak u naduwe̩ chuche̩ amone̩ ki wewe
mose̩s muda gbo̩ko̩bo̩ jihofa o̩jo̩wñ oñ i kakini o jihofa e̩wñ chi kuwe̩do̩we̩ mutajo bamone̩we̩ ekuwe̩ nukpahiu ki nana kpai o̩wo̩ ki gbiti ko ma kwane̩ ijipti wa ma una unai taa

e̩wñ chi kabo ijipti aka kakini todu ibe bie̩ne̩ ki defuwñ oñ i ko ma dufu ki fuma kpa oj uwo oj uwo ki la fuma lie̩ beju ane̩ ile̩ te̩ murida buwe̩do̩we̩ ki kpunai te̩ ke̩bie̩ne̩i eche amone̩we̩ ki we̩

e̩ nalibekado ebraham kpai aise̩k kpai israe̩l amaduwe̩ le̩ ekuwe̩ fo̩lawe̩ onugo go̩ ñwu ma ke̩ la ka ñwu ma kakini naje̩ ñw ugbe̩me̩ wewe nyo̩gba dab awo awo ojale oñ ane̩ komi ko̩lawñi du nadu ñw ugbe̩me̩ tak i ache̩wñ oguma ogbegbele̩
tak i wo̩ jihofa ugbo e̩bie̩ne̩ ki nibe ka ki ache amone̩wñ le̩
taku mose̩s murida gwo̩ru uwo le̩ tane̩ alo ibenu meji le̩ jo̩wo̩wñ alo ki che̩ko̩ eju mejeji i che o̩wo̩kawñ kpo̩wo̩ ekejiwñ che̩ko̩
alo le̩ la chuko̩lo̩ ko̩jo̩ che inawñ la china ko̩jo̩ ko̩ inawñ chewane̩ o̩la alo le̩
taku jo̩shua gbekuku amone̩ ku ma jakpogu le̩ oñ i ka ñwu mose̩s kakini ekuku ogu def uruwai
oñ i kakini i cho̩ga echi todu edu ku ma du n i la chogu ekpa todu edu ku ma du ma n chai ekuku abo ku ma jakeli oñ nagbo̩i
tak i lewatu abu ki lewa me̩ru uru le̩ ababa ki la fo̩mokuno̩ ku ma da le̩ li kpai ido ku ma jata uwe̩do̩ mose̩s mutajo oñ i ma lo le̩ ko rikpolo bo̩wo̩wñ te̩ i la fu kpo̩fo̩ e̩re̩ uwo o̩mo̩
tak i mo̩mokuno̩ ku ma da le̩ du i la fu gujo ef una tak i fu no̩ efulu oñ i fu buru ej omi tak i je̩ ñw amo̩ma israe̩l ñmo̩
taku mose̩s ka ñw aro̩n kakini ab amone̩i che̩ ke̩ fadure inainai fa buma oji ma taa
tak aro̩n kakini uwe̩do̩ odumi ki tajo n uwe̩ chema amone̩i ke̩do̩ma chekado e̩wñ e̩bie̩ne̩ eche
todu ama ka ñwu mi kakini famo̩jo̩ che ñw a ku ma atuwa o̩gba todu i chemose̩s ki ko wa kwane̩ ijipti dufu wa le̩ a mema abu kowñ le n
tak u ka ñwu ma kakini e̩ne̩ du ki no̩jamalia ki fu jada wa taku ma mu ko wa ñwu mi oñ u mu ko rikpolo nyuna tak o̩mokuno̩i kwo̩mo̩ dufu wa
tak e̩gba ku mose̩s li kamone̩ le̩ mofema du to̩fe̩ todu aro̩n je̩ ñwu ma dofema to̩fe̩ ki mud ubio̩la ugbo ame̩nebima
taku mose̩s kwodago alaku uru le̩ oñ i kakini e̩ne̩ chabo jihofa i ki wugbo mi tak o̩chaka amo̩ma e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ lifai fo̩lama do̩ jeju jugbowñ

tak i ka ñwu ma kakini abu ku jihofa o̩jo̩ eisrae̩l aka de̩ kakini e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ ki do̩kwo̩chageliwñ tachala ki talaku alaku ale ugbo du ef urui ke̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ ki kpo̩mayewñ ke̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ ki la kpa e̩ne̩ umawñ ke̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ ki kpa ekejiwñ
tak amo̩ma lifai che teju o̩la mose̩s oku one̩ ki wane̩ o̩jo̩ le̩ dabu e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ icham nyo̩gwo̩ko̩ me̩ta
mose̩s la ka kakini me̩ ke̩wñ nyo̩wo̩me̩ e̩ko̩ todu jihofa eñinii e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ kobo̩mawñ kpai o̩mayewñ todu ki de̩nyo̩ ñwu me̩ eñinii
oñ i lewatu o̩jo̩ñwawñ mose̩s ka ñw amone̩ le̩ kakini me̩ fadure inaina ta me̩ ifai tak u nate̩gu nyugbo jihofa ikani i ne̩wñ ku nache ki abadureme̩ ma
abe̩le̩ mose̩s mudabi nyugbo jihofa i kakini aaya amone̩i fadure inaina ta me̩ ma la famo̩jo̩ o̩jamalia che ñw o̩lama
i muda che̩wñ ki duwe̩ e̩do̩ e̩ dadurema tinyo̩ i ma dabe̩le̩ n oko nagbabe̩i ke̩ ki fumi kpalu bef ibukuwe̩ ke̩ ko̩ le̩ te̩
jihofa muda ka ñwu mose̩s kakini e̩ne̩ ki du mi re e̩ne̩ le̩ oñ nakpalu kwef ibukumi
lo fai ke̩ ne̩ amone̩ le̩ nyugbo ku ko̩la ñw e̩ le̩ go onuche̩mi atuwe̩ o̩gba ama o̩jo̩ ku nawa fejudo ma nawa kpai adurema edu numa oji
oñ jihofa famone̩ le̩ gwoda todabu ku ma fo̩mokuno̩ le̩ da owñ chekaro̩n che le̩
mose̩s nachologu tod abo israe̩l alo waa
taku jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini kwo bemi te̩ alo uwe̩ kpai amone̩ ke̩ ko kwane̩ ijipti dufu wa le̩ ke̩ nyane̩ komi go̩ ñw ebraham kpai aise̩k kpai jeko̩b kakini ugbe̩we̩ oñ nadu ñw u
omi la akponuche̩ tuwe̩ o̩gba oñ u nane abo kenan kpai abo amo̩r kpai abo he̩t kpai abo pe̩re̩z kpai abo hifai kpai abo je̩bius bo̩mo̩ te̩
e̩ ki mute̩gu nyane̩ ugbo komi e̩nya kpai iño̩ acha omi muda atalumejiwe̩ te̩gu alo n tode̩gba ku fe̩ lie̩ ej o̩na le̩ todu uwe̩ chamone̩ ko̩lo̩we̩ lo dago
tak e̩gba kamone̩ le̩ gbo̩ inabali e̩bie̩ne̩ ki de̩ ma kwodaido̩ e̩ne̩ du la ke̩wñ ijaga nyo̩la n

todu jihofa ka ñwu mose̩s kakini e̩ ka ñw amo̩ma israe̩l kakini ame̩ chamone̩ ko̩lo̩ma che̩lo dago iche̩wñ komi ma talumejiwe̩ alo iminitikate u ma fe̩ lie̩ todule̩ fai e̩ name̩wñ ijagawe̩ ko jane̩ bo̩lawe̩ te̩ ku fe̩wñ ku nachuwe̩ ma
todule̩ amo̩ma israe̩l me̩wñ ijagama gwo̩ bo̩lama te̩ hioko akwo uwo ho̩re̩b le̩ gbogbo alo
mose̩s la te̩tafunyabo le̩ ta ejo̩do̩da uruma owewñ kpai uru le̩ chete̩ jiji oñ i doduwñ ko̩ unyabo ujeju oñ e̩ne̩ du ki tene jihofa adufu nyugbo unyabo ujeju ki do̩do̩da uru le̩
tak i lewatu e̩gba du ku mose̩s dufu nyugbo unyabo le̩ amone̩ le̩ chaka kwane̩ oñ e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ dago alugbo̩na unyabo ewñ ma la fejuma bu mose̩s le gbogbo tak i mugudu tef unyabo
oñ e̩gba ku mose̩s mugudu tef unyabo akpa ki dago waala le̩ nagwo̩ru wane̩ ki dago alugbo̩na unyabo taku jihofa ako̩la ñwu mose̩s
oñ e̩gba kamone̩ le̩ du li abu kakpa le̩ dago waala alugbo̩na unyabo amone̩ le̩ chaka nakwane̩ adojikane̩ e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ che alugbo̩na unyabo ewñ
abe̩le̩ eju kpareju oñ jihofa ko̩la ñwu mose̩s alu kone̩ ako̩la kpai onukuwñ tak i mudabi tef uru ama jo̩shua o̩ma nun okolobia ki ache e̩wñ ñw u le̩ muda kwo bunyabo le̩ te̩ n

taku mose̩s ka ñwu jihofa kakini go ta uwe̩ ka ñwu mi kakini mamone̩i ko te̩gu wa e̩ la je̩ ñwu mi ma e̩ne̩ kuwe̩ akpuche̩ lebumi n e̩ la ka ñwu mi kakini u chema uwe̩ u chema odu ke̩ ko uwe̩ ño̩ che̩ne̩ ku nali eju
todule̩ narodubuwe̩ fai iche̩wñ ke̩ li mi eju mak e̩ ko̩no̩nawe̩ ña mi komi ki fuwe̩ ma ku ma alu ku nale ke̩ li mi eju e̩ ki ño̩ fejuwo̩ ka kuche̩ amone̩i chamone̩we̩

oñ i noli akesia foli ugbo̩lo e̩luwñ chutodu akatakpo o̩woka uña ugugu le̩

i la che oli ugbo̩lo̩ ki dalumeji ki tunyu alumeji akatakpo akatakpo akwo̩wo̩kawñ gbogbo to̩wo̩ ekeji
tak i fo̩jamalia wenyakatakpo akatakpo le̩ i no̩jamalia che elikawñ todu ki chugbo koli ugbo̩lo̩wñ atunyu i laño̩ fo̩jamalia wenyu oli ugbo̩lo̩wñ ge̩
tak i nodufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ che ukpo ugbeju le̩ amiche̩rub jo̩lawñ uko̩lo̩wñ chuko̩lo̩ o̩ka
tak i foli urane̩ akesia me̩le̩ fa toduwñ i la do̩jamalia wenyu uko̩wñ cho̩jamalia i laño̩ fo̩ka ajifa me̩le̩ da toduwñ
i ño̩ fukpo uro̩na che todu alugbo̩na unyabo le̩ i chodufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ uko̩lo̩ e̩ne̩ ki achiya nyukpo jo̩lawñ
manyoli urane̩wñ me̩lu kpai uko̩wñ i ko̩jamalia wenyojiwñ oli ugbo̩lo̩wñ ate̩ cho̩jamalia o̩kawñ me̩lu ki jofewñ muda chebijeikpa
akpati alo kpai ugugu unye̩do̩ le̩
oñ be̩zale̩l noli akesia che akpati le̩ ujijiwñ chohibo̩wo̩ meji nyukpe̩reji unabe̩wñ la chohibo̩wo̩ka nyukpereji o̩gbawñ la chohibo̩wo̩ka nyukpe̩reji
i la ko̩jamalia ki de̩ hiolo bo̩lawñ ma tejefu tejo̩do̩da oñ i fo̩jamalia gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ ki du lametiwñ daka
tak i felika o̩jamalia me̩le̩ da todu e̩re̩wñ me̩le̩ elika meji la jo̩wo̩kawñ elika meji omune̩ la jo̩wo̩ ekejiwñ
tak i noli akesia fa oli ugbo̩lo̩wñ oñ i ko̩jamalia wenyu
i la moli ugbo̩lo̩ ko tunyelika akolo akpati le̩ ku ma gwo̩nyu anakpati le̩
oñ i no̩jamalia hiolo che ugugu unye̩do̩ ujijiwñ chohibo̩wo̩ meji nyukpe̩reji unabe̩wñ la chohibo̩wo̩ka nyukpe̩reji
tak i no̩jamalia gwu amiche̩rub meji i gwu jo̩ o̩wo̩ afida ugugu unye̩do̩ le̩ meji
che̩rubka la do̩wo̩ afidawñ kekeleka che̩rub ekeji la do̩wo̩ afidawñ kekele ekeji i miche̩rub du che alukate kpai ugugu unye̩do̩ le̩ o̩wo̩wñ mejeji
amiche̩rub le̩ la fikama nadala ate̩ ikama la boji ugugu unye̩do̩ ma ate̩ ma kpejuru o̩lama eju amiche̩rub la che̩kparu ugugu unye̩do̩ le̩
i ño̩ noli ake̩sia che itebulu le̩ ujijiwñ la chohibo̩wo̩ meji unabe̩wñ la chohibo̩wo̩ka o̩gbawñ la chohibo̩wo̩ka nyukpe̩re̩ji
i la mo̩jamalia hiolo ko bo̩lawñ ma oñ i fo̩jamalia gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ ki du lametiwñ daka
i la no̩jamalia fo̩gba bu nyetiwñ daka unabe̩ o̩gbawñ chadaba o̩wo̩ka tak i fo̩jamalia gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ ki du lametiwñ daka
tak i felika o̩jamalia me̩le̩ da toduwñ oñ i melika le̩ ko tunyukawñ me̩le̩ ugbo e̩re̩wñ me̩le̩
elika le̩ me̩ru o̩gbawñ ugbo ku ma doli ugbo̩lo̩ tunyu ku ma ne̩ itebulu le̩ de̩
i noli akesia fa ugbo̩lo̩ oli ku ma du ne̩ itebulu le̩ oñ i fo̩jamalia wenyu
tak i no̩jamalia hiolo che̩wñ eku ki ajo̩ oji itebulu le̩ ugbawñ kpai ucha todu otulalewñ kpai ago iche̩bo̩wñ kpai ukpawñ ku ma ane̩ domi iche̩bo̩ danyoji e̩wñ iche̩bo̩
i ño̩ ne̩ o̩jamalia hiolo chakete le̩ egwu i gwu e̩re̩wñ kpoliwñ akpowñ kpe̩buwñ kpai ododowñ chalukate kpai owñ
e̩to̩wñ ki ta dufu akolowñ mejeji che̩fa e̩to̩ akete le̩ me̩ta kado akolowñ o̩wo̩ka e̩to̩ me̩ta omune̩ la kado akolo akete le̩ o̩wo̩ ekeji

e̩buwñ me̩ta ku ma che dab ikoko almo̩nd manyakpowñ kpai ododowñ kado e̩to̩wñ oka e̩buwñ me̩ta kti ma che dabu ikoko almo̩nd manyakpowñ kpai o̩do̩do̩wñ kado e̩to̩ ekeji—abe̩le̩ i che todu e̩to̩ me̩fa ki ta dufu kwef akete le̩
oñ ago me̩le̩ ku ma che dab ikoko almo̩nd jo̩la oli akete le̩ onugo manyakpowñ kpai ododowñ
akpo laño̩ dofe ugbo ke̩to̩ meji e̩ji ta kwo abe̩le̩ i de̩ tod e̩to̩wñ me̩fa
akpowñ kpai e̩to̩wñ chalukate kpai owñ o̩chakawñ chuko̩lo̩ ku ma no̩jamalia hiolo gwu alukate
i no̩jamalia hiolo che agegewñ mebie kpai alapawñ kpai e̩wñ kalapa le̩ ajo̩ efuwñ
o̩jamalia hiolo alu tale̩ntka i du che owñ kpai ane̩wñ chaka
i la noli akesia che ubo̩ ku ma gu e̩wñ ki akpo le̩ jo̩ ojiwñ ujijiwñ cho̩hibo̩wo̩ka unabe̩wñ ño̩ cho̩hibo̩wo̩ka akolowñ me̩le̩ chokujo̩ o̩gbawñ la cho̩hibo̩wo̩ meji igbawñ la chalukate kpai owñ
oñ i mo̩jamalia hiolo ko bo̩lawñ ma tojiwñ takolowñ daka kpai igbawñ oñ i fo̩jamalia gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ lametiwñ daka
i ño̩ fe̩lika o̩jamalia meji che toduwñ o̩gane̩ o̩jamalia ku ma gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ lametiwñ le̩ ugbo ukawñ meji akolowñ meji ki chugbo kugbo̩lo̩ oli atunyu ku ma ne̩
i la noli ake̩sia fa ugbo̩lo̩ oli le̩ oñ i fo̩jamalia wenyu
i laño̩ fekpo ki afo̩ ku ma du bato̩la le̩ che ge̩ kpai otulale hiolo ku ma gujo ki ne̩wñ kwe̩ kwe̩ kwe̩ ki akpo che i che alu ke̩ne̩ ki cho̩ka otulale ache
ane̩ ef unyabo le̩
i ño̩ noli akesia che ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ e̩gujo ge̩ ujijiwñ cho̩hibo̩wo̩ me̩lu unabe̩wñ la chohibo̩wo̩ me̩lu akolowñ me̩le̩ chokujo̩ o̩gbawñ la chohibo̩wo̩ me̩ta
i la figba che oji ukawñ me̩le̩ igbawñ la chalukate kpai owñ i la nebijeikpa wenyo̩lawñ
oñ i fe̩wñ eku ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ che chaka uchawñ kpai uko̩che̩wñ kpai ugbawñ kpai uko̩wñ ku ma du tate̩la kpai e̩wñ kelulu awane̩ jojiwñ o̩chaka e̩wñ e̩kuwñ le̩ i nebijeikpa che
i la febijeikpa gwu kpataka ki che̩gudu e̩gudu dab iga tod ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ i che̩hiwane̩ baluwñ te̩ talumejiwñ
i nebijeikpa felika me̩le̩ da todu uka me̩le̩ ebijeikpa kpataka le̩ ki chugbo ku ma ko ugbo̩lo̩ oli le̩ tunyu
i la noli akesia gbe̩ ugbo̩lo̩ oliwñ oñ i febijeikpa wenyu
tak i ko ugbo̩lo̩ oli le̩ tunyelika ki jo̩ akolo ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ ku ma ne̩ i nakatakpo che kefuwñ ki te̩ ofo
oñ i nebijeikpa che ukpachi ugwo̩wo̩wñ e̩wñ uguguwñ laño̩ chebijeikpa ge̩ ogigo abobule̩ ku ma jeju jalugbo̩na unyabo ujeju le̩ oñ i ne̩ che
tak i fologbowñ bu ukpo ku ma du bologbo o̩pata o̩wo̩ awo̩to̩wñ chukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ i chohibo̩wo̩ ogu me̩lu
oli urane̩wñ chogu o̩kawñ chogu ebijeikpa i che uko̩ oli urane̩wñ kpai ugbo̩lo̩wñ ate̩ muda chajifa
o̩patawñ o̩wo̩ awohi ño̩ chohibo̩wo̩ ogu me̩lu oli urane̩wñ chogu o̩kawñ chogu ebijeikpa i che uko̩ oli urane̩wñ kpai ugbo̩lo̩wñ ate̩ muda chajifa
ukpo ku ma la ta jo̩wo̩ olane̩ la chohibo̩wo̩ ooje oli urane̩wñ che̩gwa o̩kawñ la che̩gwa uko̩ oli urane̩ le̩ kpai ugbo̩lo̩wñ ate̩ muda chajifa
todu o̩gbawñ eju oloduduwñ i chohibo̩wo̩ ooje
ukpowñ o̩wo̩ka chohibo̩wo̩ me̩gwe̩lu oli urane̩wñ che̩ta okawñ la che̩ta
abe̩le̩ i ño̩ de̩ o̩wo̩ ekejiwñ o̩wo̩ emi kpai o̩wo̩ ej ano̩mo̩ alu ologbo le̩ ukpo ku ma du bu chohibo̩wo̩ me̩gwe̩lu oli urane̩wñ che̩ta o̩kawñ la che̩ta
ukpo du ku ma ko bologbo le̩ daka chukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju
o̩ka koli urane̩ le̩ atunyu la chebijeikpa uko̩ oli urane̩ le̩ kpai ugbo̩lo̩wñ ate̩ muda chajifa ebije ku ma gwu tunyojiwñ ño̩ chajifa oli urane̩ ologbo le̩ du nugbo̩lo̩ ajifa ate̩ ta tomune̩

ukpo uro̩na alaku ologbo le̩ chuko̩lo̩ e̩ne̩ ki cho̩ka iya eche nyukpo odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai line̩n ku ma hi reju ujijiwñ la chohibo̩wo̩ ogu o̩gbawñ owñ cho̩wo̩ unabe̩wñ chohibo̩wo̩ me̩lu owñ chalu kukpo ku ma du bologbo le̩ de̩
oli urane̩wñ la che̩le̩ o̩kawñ me̩le̩ chebijeikpa uko̩wñ la chajifa e̩wñ ki che̩gwu tojiwñ kpai ugbo̩lo̩wñ ku ma du no̩ lale ño̩ chajifa ge̩
ale uña ugugu le̩ chaka kpai eologbowñ ki lo daka chebijeikpa
aluka e̩wñ todu uña ugugu le̩ de̩ owñ chuña ugugu eibenu le̩ ku ma kalukawñ alu ku mose̩s dalu ñwu ma le̩ owñ chuko̩lo̩ kabo lifai ku ma jef o̩wo̩ itamar o̩ma aro̩n atama che
oñ be̩zale̩l o̩ma uri ki cho̩ma he̩r abo o̩lo̩pu juda fe̩wñ du ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s chekpa

e̩ne̩ ki la manyowñ choholiab o̩ma ahisamak ki chabo o̩lo̩pu dan owñ che̩ne̩ ki akina nyo̩la e̩wñ o̩ka uko̩lo̩ ehi kpai echiya nyo̩la ukpo odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo line̩n ku ma hi reju i che

o̩jamalia du ku ma ne̩ chuko̩lo̩ le̩ owñ chuko̩lo̩ uña kiafo̩ le̩ chaka owñ cho̩jamalia ku ma ko wa miejo le̩ o̩chakawñ che tale̩nt ogu nyoke me̩la kpai she̩ke̩l e̩te̩gwa chi icham owñ chishe̩ke̩l euña kiafo̩ le̩
ajifa abo ku ma kaluka ef abo o̩gbadu le̩ la che tale̩nt ogu me̩lu kpai she̩ke̩l icham nyo̩gwo̩ko̩ nyogume̩lu mebie nye̩te̩gwa nyoke me̩lu alu ki she̩ke̩l euña kiafo̩ de̩

e̩ne̩ka ne̩ be̩kaka tod ojiwñ owñ chukpe̩reji she̩ke̩l alu ki she̩ke̩l euña kiafo̩ le̩ de̩ i chutodu e̩ne̩ du ki lale tef abo ku ma kaluka e̩ne̩ du ko̩do̩wñ jo̩ ogu owñ chaboke̩le̩ icham nyo̩gwo̩ko̩ ugbo ulo̩gwa nyoke meta one̩ oli me̩gwaka nojiwñ
ajifa alu tale̩nt ogu me̩lu le̩ la chutodu ku ma ne̩ da o̩ka ki jofe uña kiafo̩ le̩ kpai o̩ka ki jofe ukpo ugbejuwñ o̩ka ogu me̩lu che tale̩nt ogu me̩lu tale̩nt oka cho̩kaka
taku she̩ke̩l icham nyo̩gwo̩ko̩ nyogume̩lu mebie nye̩te̩gwa nyoke me̩lu le̩ i muko chuko̩ todu oli urane̩wñ oñ i mu du gwu tunyojiwñ tak i mugbo̩lo̩wñ ate̩ ko ta to̩
ebijeikpa ku ma kowa miejo le̩ chalu tale̩nt e̩te̩gwa manyu she̩ke̩l icham me̩ta
ele̩ i muko che o̩ka o̩ka todu alu o̩na unyabo ujeju le̩ kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ ebijeikpa le̩ kpai ebijeikpa kpataka ki che̩gudu e̩gudu ki de̩ efuwñ kpai e̩wñ eku eubo̩ iche̩bo̩ le̩ chaka
kpai o̩ka o̩ka ki la je̩re̩ ologbo le̩ daka kpai o̩ka o̩ka alu o̩na ologbo le̩ kpai ale uña ugugu le̩ chaka kpai ale ologbo ki ledaka
e̩wñ o̩la amatama
oñ ma modufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa le̩ ko ga e̩wñ o̩la ku ma nyi ache e̩wñ ef uña kiafo̩ ma fe̩wñ o̩la kiafo̩ ga todu aro̩n alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
tak i no̩jamalia kpai odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ che e̩fo̩d le̩
ma la fo̩jamalia gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ oñ ma fu kpana mie̩le̩ mie̩le̩ ku ma du chiya o̩ka o̩ka nyodufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai line̩n ku ma hi reju le̩
ma fe̩wñ ojikawñ che ku ma du gamo̩ etiwñ meji chegamo̩

ma no̩jamalia kpai odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ che e̩wñ ujiñmi e̩fo̩d ki do̩lawñ ku ma ne̩ damu mo̩ ki chalukate kpai owñ uko̩lo̩wñ chokate alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
taku ma fuko̩lo̩ okuta one̩ks le̩ che ma fo̩jamalia da nyu oñ ma fina ko̩ nyu alu ku ma kma nye̩wñ uhiuko̩ alu kodu amo̩ma e̩ne̩ke̩le̩ israe̩l de̩
tak i fu gamo̩ ukpo o̩j ika ee̩fo̩d le̩ ki che okuta urewa todu amo̩ma israe̩l alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
tak i fe̩wñ ube̩do̩ma che uko̩lo̩wñ chuko̩lo̩ o̩ka alu kuko̩lo̩ e̩fo̩d le̩ de̩ i cho̩jamalia kpai odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ che̩da bie̩
ago̩go̩wñ me̩le̩ chokujo̩ ma fe̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ che ki cheji ne̩do̩ o̩lawñ ujijiwñ cho̩chali o̩wo̩ka unabe̩wñ la cho̩chali o̩wo̩ka e̩ji ne̩do̩ omune̩
oñ ma fokuta ganyu o̩gba o̩gba ugbo me̩le̩ o̩gbakawñ che sardius kpai topaz kpai karbunke̩l ele̩ cho̩gba ejodudu
o̩gba ekeji la che e̩me̩rald kpai safaya kpai daimo̩nd
o̩gba e̩ke̩ta la che jesint kpai age̩t kpai ame̩tist
o̩gba e̩ke̩le̩ la che be̩re̩l kpai one̩ks kpai jaspe̩r ma fo̩jamalia danyokuta ugbo ki jo̩ le̩
okuta le̩ la jo̩ alu kodu odu amo̩ma israe̩l de̩ e̩gwe̩ji i che alu koduma de̩ i che̩ko̩ nyu dab e̩wñ uhiuko̩ e̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ne̩ dalu koduwñ de̩ todu o̩lo̩pu me̩gweji le̩
taku ma fiyagba che to̩la e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ dabe̩ne̩ kiku uko̩lo̩wñ cho̩jamalia hiolo ku ma fuba
oñ ma no̩jamalia chagbamune̩wñ meji kpai elika o̩jamalia meji taku ma felika meji le̩ gamo̩ akolo e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ meji
taku ma miyagba o̩jamalia meji ku ma ba le̩ ko tunyelika meji ki jeti e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩
ma la koji iyagba ku ma ba meji ki bo̩ jane̩ tunyagbamune̩ meji le̩ abe̩le̩ ma fu gamo̩ ukpo oj ika e̩fo̩d le̩ e̩j o̩gbawñ
taku ma felika o̩jamalia meji da oñ ma fu gamo̩ iba e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ mejeji eliwñ ki me̩ru e̩fo̩d ejefu oñ ma du ne
ma la felika o̩jamalia meji da oñ ma fu gamo̩ o̩wo̩ o̩gane̩ ukpo ojika e̩fo̩d le̩ ejefuwñ e̩jo̩gbawñ me̩ru ugbo ku ma ko gbako omune̩ ate̩ ñw e̩wñ ujiñmi ee̩fo̩d le̩
taku ma mo̩jaja odufa ko tunyelika e̩wñ ube̩do̩ma kpai elika ee̩fo̩d ku ma fuji momune̩ todu ki noji e̩wñ ujiñmi ee̩fo̩d le̩ ke̩wñ ube̩do̩ma le̩ ki we etachi be̩fo̩d te̩ alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
i laño̩ fotogbo e̩fo̩d le̩ hi o̩chakawñ chodufa
e̩gudu alumeji otogbo le̩ dalu ku ma do̩fa adika ogu ma fe̩gba du nalu e̩guduwñ daka ki we efana
taku ma ne̩ odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa kpai ukpo line̩n kowuwñ che̩da bie̩ ga meti otogbo le̩ dab e̩ro oli ku ma do̩ ko̩ po̩me̩grane̩t
ma laño̩ ne̩ o̩jamalia hiolo da ilo ilo oñ ma milo le̩ ko tunyagbagba po̩me̩grane̩t le̩ le̩re̩ otogbo le̩ daka ki kpe̩gwa nyu po̩me̩grane̩t le̩
ilo kpai po̩me̩grane̩t ilo kpai po̩me̩grane̩t neti e̩re̩ otogbo le̩ daka ku ma nyi ache e̩wñma alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
oñ ma nukpo line̩n ki che̩hi reju gafe̩ todu aro̩n kpai amo̩mawñ
alawoniwñ laño̩ che ukpo line̩n ki che̩hi reju o̩tajia ki fe̩reju ño̩ che ukpo line̩n ki che̩hi reju ichakawñ che line̩n efufu ku ma hi reju ku ma dowuwñ bie̩
e̩wñ ujiñmiwñ la che line̩n ku ma hi reju kowuwñ cheda bie̩ kpai odufa kpai odufa ekpikpa kpai ekpikpa uko̩lo̩ e̩ne̩ ki achiya nyukpo jo̩lawñ alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
oñ ma fo̩jamalia hiolo gwu pe̩te̩ke̩ todu ike̩be̩ kiafo̩ le̩ ma la folubutu ko̩ nyu alu ku ma kina nye̩wñ uhiuko̩ kakini efo̩ ñwu jihofa
taku ma fowu odufa daku nyu ku ma du ji manyalawoni ate̩wñ alu ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s
abe̩le̩ ma fuko̩lo̩ uña ugugu eunyabo ujeju le̩ che kpa amo̩ma israe̩l la fu che teju alu du ki jihofa ñwa ñwu mose̩s abe̩le̩ ma che
taku ma muña ugugu le̩ ko wugbo mose̩s unyabo kpai ane̩wñ du kpai atanyiwñ kpai akatakpowñ kpai oli ugbo̩lo̩wñ kpai oli urane̩wñ kpai o̩kawñ
kpai año̩ okolo ku ma hi ekpikpa ku ma ko bojiwñ ate̩ ma kpai año̩ e̩la omi ku ma ko boji ele̩ ma kpai ukpo ugbeju
kpai akpati ibenu le̩ manyoli ugbo̩lo̩wñ kpai ugugu unye̩do̩
itebuluwñ kpai e̩wñ ekuwñ chaka kpai akala eeju le̩
akete ku ma no̩jamalia hiolo che kpai agegewñ kagegewñ tala jojiwñ aro̩ne aro̩ne kpai e̩wñ ekuwñ chaka kpai ekpo todu ugane̩
kpai ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ eo̩jamalia kpai ekpo ku ma du bato̩la kpai otulale ku ma gujo ki akpo kpai ukpo uro̩na tod alo̩na unyabo le̩
ubo̩ iche̩bo̩ eebijeikpa kpai ebijeikpa kpataka ki che̩gudu e̩gudu ki defuwñ oli ugbo̩lo̩wñ kpai e̩wñ ekuwñ chaka ukpachi ugwo̩wo̩ kpai e̩wñ uguguwñ
ukpo ku ma du bologbo oli urane̩wñ kpai o̩kawñ kpai ukpo uro̩na alu ologbo le̩ ikuwñ kpai alewñ kpai e̩wñ eku chaka ku ma ne̩ che e̩wñ ef uña ugugu owñ chutod unyabo ujeju le̩
e̩wñ o̩la ku ma hi ku ma nyi ache e̩wñ ef uña kiafo̩ kpai afe̩ kiafo̩ todu aro̩n atama le̩ kpai afe̩ todu amo̩mawñ ku ma ne̩ che e̩wñ amatama

jọshua
ọjọ jẹ ñwu jọshua koji mosẹs

ugbo du kadaba ẹrẹwẹ manẹ uwẹ omi du ñwu alu ku ka ñwu mosẹs lẹ
akwo ajẹtachi kpai anẹ lẹbanọn kidẹ gbogbo wohimini elile owñ chohimini yufretis kpai anẹ abo hẹt chaka gbogbo wohimini elile ọwọ olanẹ elẹ chalọmẹwẹ

ma dabi kẹpi da
adiko lẹ jihofa ka ñwu jọshua kakini mẹ du okuta ọmu che abẹ ñw ọlamẹ ku mẹ dabi kẹpi abo israẹl da onukeji
abẹlẹ jọshua fabẹ okuta ọmu che ñw ọlawñ oñ i kẹpi abo israẹl da gibeathaaralọt
ẹwñ ki chi ku jọshua la duma ẹpi lẹ dẹ abokẹlẹ du ku ma jef abo ku ma kw ijipti dufu wa lẹ owñ chabokẹlẹ ku ma jogu chaka leku ej ọna ef ajẹtachi abu ku ma kwijipti dufu wa
todu amonẹ du ku ma kwọmọ dufu wa fẹpi da ama amonẹ du ku ma bi ej ọna ef ajẹtachi abu ku ma kwijipti dufu wa lẹ la dẹpi ta n

todu abo israẹl tale ef ajẹtachi lẹ ọdọ ọgbọ meji gbogbo taku ma fabo ichi lẹ du owñ chabokẹlẹ ku ma jogu ku ma kw ijipti dufu wa lẹ liẹ kpa todabu ku ma ma netiromu jihofa n owñ chabo ki jihofa fugọ ñwu ma ka ki ajẹ ñwu ma fejuma do anẹ eki jihofa gọ ñw amatama ka ki adu ñw ma anẹ komi ẹnya kpai iñọ acha efuwñ
taku jọshua famọmama ki ko kwanẹ koji ma ẹpi da todu ẹpima chodukulu ta abu ku ma ma duma ẹpi ej ọna lẹ n
oñ i lewatu ẹgba ku ma fabo ichi lẹ ẹpi da kpa kama kwojọ ẹguma ef uru lẹ gbogbo tak i biẹ
taku jihofa ka ñwu jọshua kakini omi fina ijipti li bumẹ ọla tẹ eñinii mẹ todulẹ ma dodu ugbo ki dẹ kọ gilgal gbogbo teñini
ma felaloji jẹ
oñ abo israẹl kworu gilgal lẹ ma la felaloji jẹ anẹ ọjọ ẹkẹgwẹlẹ ochu lẹ ef egbili jẹriko
tak ama fọka eechi anẹ lẹ jẹ ọjọñwa elaloji gbagẹdẹ owñ chakala kọjọwu ma dọ n kpai akakpa ẹrọ
taku mana lẹ we ọjọñwawñ owñ chabu ku ma fẹwñ oko anẹ lẹ jẹ oñ abo israẹl ñọ nẹ mana lẹ gẹ n chai ẹro anẹ kenan ma jẹ ọdọ lẹ

oñ i lewatu ẹgba ki jọshua mẹru jẹriko lẹ ki la chi ejuwñ nyatẹ ago ẹ la go ẹnẹkẹlẹka dago kpenyu ọbẹchageliwñ chẹwọ nọwọ taki jọshua nyugbowñ aka ñw u kakini ẹnẹwa ẹ che abẹk ẹ def abo ku ma fuwa kpama
oñ i kakini ọda ama todu ku chagboji abogu jihofa oñ u wai taku jọshua lewa feju banẹ ma oñ i dojikanẹ i la ka ñw u kakini ab odumi aka ñw aduwñi
tak agboji abogu jihofa lẹ ka ñwu jọshua kakini mẹdawẹ gwọ bẹrẹwẹ tẹ todu ugbo kẹ dago lẹ afọ taku jọshua fabẹlẹ che
ma fu jẹriko kpọfọ
alaku jẹriko chaka la chere ma mukodowñ ko tunyu todu abo israẹl ẹnẹ du adufu n ẹnẹ du la agudu wejefu n
oñ jihofa ka ñwu jọshua kakini go u mijẹriko du tuwẹ ọwọ mẹ kpai onuwñ kpai amẹnugbitiwñ ku ma nuwohi
oñ anẹ ale ewo lẹ daka abokẹlẹ ku ma jogu chaka ale ewo lẹ daka onuka abẹlẹ uwẹ ache gbogbo nyọjọ mẹfa
oñ amatama mebie anẹ ọkakachi ọga echi mebie ale rọgba akpati lẹ tak ọjọ ẹkebiewñ ama ale ewo lẹ daka onu mebie oñ amatama anọkakachima afa
tak i awatu ẹgba ku ma fa igba ọga echi lẹ taa kamẹ la gbọ omu ọkakachi lẹ amonẹ du anukwa akwa nana tak ọdọ aku ewo lẹ agulọ banẹ ma oñ ẹnẹnẹnẹnẹ efu amonẹ lẹ afẹdọ kẹdọwñ atẹgu tọgbawñ alo
abẹlẹ jọshua ọma nun lẹ famatama dọ wa oñ i ka ñwu ma kakini mẹ makpati alo lẹ du tak amatama mebie ki nọkakachi ọga echi mebie rọgba akpati jihofa lẹ
tak i ka ñw amonẹ lẹ kakini mẹ kanyi alo ku mẹ le ewo lẹ daka ku mẹ jẹ ñw abokẹlẹ kọlama chẹmu ogu ku ma lale rọgba akpati jihofa
oñ alu ki jọshua ka ñw amonẹ lẹ amatama mebie ku ma nọkakachi ọga echi mebie ọgba jihofa lẹ le rọgba oñ ma nọkakachima afa akpati alo jihofa la tuma ubi
oñ abokẹlẹ ku ma mọla ogu le rọgba amatama ku ma fa ọkakachi lẹ oñ abo ki dubi takpati ubi ma nọkakachi afa abu ku ma alo
jọshua la ñwa ñw amonẹ lẹ kakini amẹ ki kpogu n ẹnẹ du ki gbomumẹ n ọla du ki kwef alumẹ dufu n gbogbo nyọjọ ku naka ñwu mẹ ku mẹ kpogu ẹgbalẹ taku mẹ akpogu
abẹlẹ i jẹ ñw akpati jihofa ki le ewo lẹ daka i le onuka taku ma lewa uru lẹ oñ ma kworu
taki jọshua takpa kwanẹ odudu oñ amatama makpati jihofa du
dufu gẹ oñ ma muma ko jej ọdọda uru abo israẹl lẹ
taku ma fewo gujo rinyọ kpai ẹwñ du ki jefuwñ chai ajifawñ kpai ọjamaliawñ kpai ẹwñ eku ebijeikpa kpai ebije ma melẹ ko nyef akpulu ef unyi jihofa
ama jọshua fu rehab ajọkọ lẹ kpai abo unyi atawñ kpai ẹwñ du ki nẹ jadu ku ma deju oñ onobulẹ lẹ gugu alumeji abo israẹl gbogbo tojolu eñini todabu ki kamonuchẹ ki jọshua kpẹ atanẹ jẹriko lẹ maja
taku jọshua jẹ ñwu ma gọ iko lẹ kakini ama ki fẹnẹ du ki kwanẹ anọdọ jẹrikoi mu eju jihofa ẹrẹwñ ki adudanẹ chọmọgbawñ elenyọ alakuwñ edudago chudabiwñ elenyọ

ọwọma bai jọ n tod adure ekan lẹ

jọshua la fonẹ kpẹ kwo jẹriko nyi ai ki dọwọka bẹtafẹn ọwọ olodudu bẹtẹl oñ i ka ñwu ma kakini mẹ tẹgu nyọmọ atanẹ lẹ tak abokẹlẹ lẹ le natanẹ ai

oñ ma mudabi wugbo jọshua oñ ma ka ñw u kakini uwẹ ki jẹ ñw ọchaka amonẹi le n chai abokẹlẹ icham nyọgwọkọ meji abẹk ẹta ki le ku ma fai kpọfọ ẹ ki jẹ ñw amonẹi chaka ki chọbata anyọmọ n todu abo lẹ wewe n

taku jọshua fẹwñ ọlawñ fana oñ i lewa feju rọ banẹ ma ọgba akpati jihofa gbogbo tolanẹ owñ kpai abogijo israẹl taku ma febutu gba nyọlama oji

o ondu abu naka abu kabo israẹl murida ramẹnebima ọgba
todu abo kenan kpai abo ku ma dodo anẹi chaka agbinabaliwñ taku ma ado nyuwa daka taku ma akoduwa da banẹilẹ tẹ oñ abuwẹ ache todu oduwẹ inainai ta

abo israẹl fadure ta ma lañọ falomi ku ñwa ñwu ma daba gẹ ma la mẹwñ ko kwef ẹwñ ku ma kojọ ñw ọjọ lẹ ma la foji ji ma ñọ dọwọ ye eju gẹ ma lañọ mẹwñ lẹ ko jef anẹ ema gẹ
todulẹ oñ amọma israẹl ma neke dago ọgba amẹnebima n oñ ma murida rọgba amẹnebima todabu kama mọlama kojọ ñw ọjọ mẹ u ñadugbo mẹ gẹ n chai ẹgba ku mẹ fẹwñ ku ma kojọ ñw ọjọ lẹ chilẹchẹ balumejimẹ tẹ

todulẹ ama ako mẹ wa ọlọpu ọlọpu odudu ọna tak abu i adẹ dẹ ọlọpu ki jihofa mu adufu wa ikpunyi ikpunyi tak ikpunyi ki jihofa mu adufu wa akwọra unyi akwọra unyi tak abo akwọra unyi ki jihofa mu adufu wa okoka
taku ma afẹnẹku jihofa mu kẹwñ ku ma dutẹ ñw ọjọ lẹ def ọwọwñ gujo towñ tẹwñ du ki nẹ todabu ki malo jihofa daba kpai todabu ki fẹwñ tuñu che efu israẹl
abẹlẹ jọshua takpa kwanẹ odudu oñ i kabo israẹl wa ọlọpu ọlọpu oñ ọla lẹ fabo ọlọpu juda mu
tak i mabo juda ko wa oñ i fabo ikpunyi zera mu tak i mabo ikpunyi zẹra kowa okoka oñ i fu zabdi mu
tak i mabo akwọra unyiwñ duwa okoke oñ i fu ekan ọma karmi ọma zabdi ọma zẹra ef ọlọpu juda mu

ẹgba ku fotogbo babilọn ọmẹmẹlẹ li ef anẹ ka ko lẹ kpai ajifa alu shẹkẹl ulọkọ kpai odukulu ọjamaliaka kuwojiwñ che shẹkẹl ooje ẹgbalẹ u chejufufuwñ oñ u mu ko ẹ la go i gwaji anẹpẹtẹ ef unyabomi lẹ ajifa la jofewñ

taku ma mu ko kwef unyabo lẹ oñ ma mu ko wugbo jọshua kpai abo israẹl chaka taku ma mu ko janẹ ọgba jihofa

taku jọshua kpai abo israẹl chaka gwọnyu ekan ọma zẹra kpai ajifa lẹ kpai otogbo kpai odukulu ọjamalia lẹ kpai amọmawñ ẹnẹkẹlẹ kpai onobulẹ kpai amọkokunọwñ kpai amọkẹkẹtẹwñ kpai amẹwñọrẹwñ egini kpai unyabowñ kpai ẹwñ du ki nẹ oñ ma mu ko wa jef ọgọ ekọr
taku jọshua kakini ab ẹ le kẹ ma chuwa uñmi n jihofa achuwẹ uñmi eñinii n tak abo israẹl chaka kokuta rọ do ma la nuna fuma gujo oñ ma kokuta rọ do ma
oñ ma mokuta re bọ oji ma dago dab ugbudu lile ki dọmọ gbogbo teñini taku jihofa rida bẹkpuna uwẹdọwñ tẹ todulẹ oñ ma dodu ugbo kidẹ kọ ọgọ ekọr gbogbo teñini
ma fai kpọfọ
taku jihofa ka ñwu jọshua kakini ẹ ki railo n ẹdọwẹ ki muda kpu n mabo ku ma jogu chaka ko lebuwẹ kẹ kwanẹ kẹ nyi ai go u monu ai kpai abowñ kpai ewowñ kpai anẹwñ ko nyuwẹ ọwọ mẹ
uwẹ ki la che ai kpai onuwñ alu kẹ che jẹriko kpai onuwñ lẹ ẹ muda manẹwñ kogu jẹ kpai amẹla abẹrẹmẹlẹwñ ko chẹwñ alujẹ ñw ọlawẹ ẹ ki kpala nyewo lẹ ejubiwñ
abẹlẹ jọshua kwanẹ kpai abo ku ma jogu chaka ku ma nyi ai taku jọshua fonẹ icham nyọgwọkọ oguẹgwa chi amẹnugbiti ku ma nuwohi lẹ oñ i jẹ ñwu ma le odu
tak i ñwa ñw ma kakini go amẹ ki kpala nyewo lẹ ejubiwñ mẹ ki le jiji bewo lẹ tẹ n ama ọlamẹ ki chẹmu chaka
tak omi kpai amonẹ ku ma jugbo mi atẹmẹrewo lẹ oñ i awatu ẹgba ku ma dufu wa kuma kobuwa alu ku ma wa che ẹgba ejodudu lẹ a ara rọgbama
tak ama dufu wa atuwa ubi gbogbo tak a fuma fa bewo lẹ tẹ todu ama akakini ma ra rọgbawa alu ku ma che ejodudu lẹ abẹlẹ a ara rọgbama
tak amẹ ki kwanẹ kwugbo ku mẹ kpala jọ lẹ ku mẹ mewo lẹ gba todu jihofa ọjọmẹ amu du tumẹ ọwọ
tak i awatu ẹgba ku mẹ mewo lẹ gba nyọwọ tak amẹ aduna tewo lẹ ku mẹ che alu ki jihofa ka lẹ mẹ go omi ñwa ñwu mẹ mẹ

tak i monẹ dabu icham nyọgwọkọ mẹlu ko oñ i jẹ ñwu ma kpala jọ agbagba bẹtẹl kpai ai ọwọ olanẹ ewo lẹ

ma kpalo kpai abo gibeọn

oñ i lewatu ẹgba kamonu du ku ma judaba jọrdan anẹ uwowñ kpai anẹ ọgọwñ ọla ohimini elile ọgba lẹbanọn lẹ gbinabaliwñ owñ chabo hẹt kpai abo amọr kpai abo kenan kpai abo pẹrẹz kpai abo hifai kpai abo jẹbius lẹ
